         notdet
;
         coordinates were not determined
;
         dual
;
         dual-space method (Sheldrick et al., 2001)
;
         iterative
;
         iterative e.g. charge flipping [Oszl\'anyi, G. and S\"uto, A. (2004).
         Acta Cryst. A60, 134-141]
;
         other
;
         a method not included elsewhere in this list
;

